  stimulus_text = 'A study was done in which researchers tried to determine the most effective method for people to conserve energy. In the study, researchers asked participants to identify the most effective action that people can take to save energy. The team then classified each action as either an efficiency (using a more efficient appliance or lightbulb) or a curtailment (using a bike or public transportation, or turning off the lights).',
